!!!
html
  head
    title
      | Chris Wagner's Blog
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    link(rel='stylesheet', type='text/css', href='/stylesheets/style.css')
    include includes/mixins
  body
    header
      h1
        a(href='/')
          | ChrisWagnerBlog.com
    .content
      block content
    .sidebar
      aside.bio
        h1 Bio
        p
          | I'm Chris Wagner, a software developer working in <a href="http://www.telerik.com">Telerik</a>'s <a href="http://www.telerik.com/services/overview.aspx">Services Team</a>.
        p
          | As it would happen, my day job and my hobbies intersect very nicely.
      aside
        h1 Categories
        ul.categories
          - each cat in categoryList
            li
              a(href=categoryUrl(cat)) #{cat}
      aside
        h1 Tags
        ul.tags
          - each tag in tagList
            li
              a(href=tagUrl(tag)) #{tag}
    footer
      p Copyright &copy; 2013 Chris Wagner.
      p Powered by <a href="http://jsantell.github.com/poet/">Poet</a>.